                    <span>I think that the book Brian's hunt was one of the best books that I have ever written. The book just kept me wanting to read. My teacher read it out loud but it felt like I was there with him this time. This book was the best book of 2004 that I have ever read. I think that I would not write so much stuff. It didn't end like I was thinking. It was the better then what I thought it would of ended. I loved the book from began to the end.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">A lone camping trip results in a wounded dog's appearance</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
